<lb n="0936a14" ed="T"/>靜慮諸行滅。有緣第二<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0936001" n="0936001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0936001" n="0936001"/>第三<anchor xml:id="end0936001"/>第四靜慮諸
